com.google.i18n.pseudolocalization.message

Class DefaultVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.i18n.pseudolocalization.message.DefaultVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessageFragmentVisitor, MessageVisitor, VariantFormVisitor, VariantFragmentVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BracketAdder, CharacterSubstituter, Expander, FakeBidi, HtmlPreserver, PigLatin

    public class DefaultVisitor
extends Object
implements MessageVisitor, MessageFragmentVisitor, VariantFormVisitor, VariantFragmentVisitor
    Default visitor which includes no-ops for all visitor methods. All methods which return sub-visitors return this.

    Most visitors should extend this class to avoid future compatibility breaks where possible.
